{"id":64724,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/中国-江苏校园斩杀案多人死伤/","date":"2010-04-29T14:50:07Z","modified":"2010-04-29T14:50:07Z","title":"中国: 江苏校园斩杀案多人死伤","content":"<div>\n<div><img src=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_43_large/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/2010-04-06_CHINA-child.JPG\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"344\" height=\"257\"></p>\n<div style=\"width:344px\">\n<div>合肥医院一名病童 </p>\n<div>Reuters</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n            作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/auteur/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%B9%E7%BA%A6%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85-%E9%BA%A6%E7%87%95%E5%BA%AD\">香港特约记者 麦燕庭</a>          </div>\n<p>中国连日发生校园砍杀案。江苏泰兴镇人民幼儿园今早(4月29日)被一名持刀男子闯入，斩伤32人受伤，包括29名幼儿、两名教师及一名保安员，其中五人伤势严重。有网民发帖说，当中四名学童不治。</p>\n<p>据《央广新闻》报道，事发早上九时半，受伤者属于幼儿园小二班的孩子。公安当场拘捕四十七岁疑凶，正调查他行凶的动机。现场亦已被封锁，家长不能进入幼儿园。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>广东湛江雷州市一间小学昨日(4月28日)亦有持刀男子闯入，斩伤十八名学生及一名教师。疑犯其后被制服，被捕时神志不清。</p>\n<p>同日，上月在福建省南平斩死斩伤十三名小学生的男子被处决。<br />\n </p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n          关键词 : <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/tag/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\">中国</a> &#8211; <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/tag/%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A\">社会</a>        </div>\n</p></div>\n<p><iframe src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~ah/f/3a0eikgr43a9jo4dqnspg01v6s/300/250?ca=1&amp;fh=280#http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinese.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%2F20100429-%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%258B%258F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259B%25AD%25E6%2596%25A9%25E6%259D%2580%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BC%25A4\" width=\"100%\" height=\"280\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/RFICN/~4/wbXeUOiLiyc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}